headline.print_headline: Hostages Seen Running Out of Sydney Siege Cafe-Live TV
headline.main: Hostages Seen Running Out of Sydney Siege Cafe-Live TV

lead_paragraph: Hostages were shown running out of a Sydney cafe at the centre of a siege on Monday, according to Channel 7 live news footage.
